name: Dynamic Active Global Dividend ETF
longDescription: In seeking to achieve its investment objectives, by investing primarily in a broadly diversified portfolio of equity securities of businesses located around the world that pay or are expected to pay a dividend or distribution. The Fund seeks to provide longterm capital growth.
